title: SQLite Expert Professional 5.3.0.334 x86/x64 !{Latest}
description:
SQLite Expert Professional 5.3.0.334 x86/x64 !{Latest}

SQLite Expert  is a powerful program that will allow you to manage and organize SQLite databases, visually show you which tables and classes work.

The user interface is convenient, but due to the lack of Russian support and a lot of customization,

not everyone will be able to figure it out, although if you work with the database, I think you can understand where and what to click.



In the main window, you can view all your databases and, if you want, you can execute your SQL scripts using the SQL Builder tab.

Choosing the right database, you will be available different tabs, each displays the necessary information.

The settings are quite sufficient, if by the nature of your activity you often have to administer databases, then I think the program is just a find.

Developer : Bogdan Ureche 
License : ShareWare 
Language : English 
OS : Windows
